<HEADLINE>
<P>
O, YOSEMITE! 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I am in love with Yosemite Valley and have been since my parents introduced me 
to it in the mid-1930s. I care very much about the preservation of our great 
natural areas such as Yosemite, and I want for them the kind of management that 
will maintain them for future generations -- but offer them for the first-hand 
enjoyment of these future generations. It takes a Curry Co. to do that. 
</P>
<P>
ROBERT M. CUTSHALL 
</P>
<P>
Pasadena 
</P>
