<P>
Pete Wilson has won the battle, but lost the war. The issue to me was a divided 
government. 
</P>
<P>
A Republican in as governor with a Democratic Legislature. Since that has 
happened, Wilson is going to find that many of his campaign promises are going 
to be derailed in the Legislature. 
</P>
