MINORITIES -- EMPLOYMENT; EMPLOYMENT DISCRIMINATION; RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; SEX 
DISCRIMINATION; HIRING QUOTAS; CIVIL RIGHTS; LABOR STATISTICS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
