<P>
Recipe; Book Review 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA111890-0253 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 310243 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 18, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
