<P>
December 2, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</CORRECTION-DATE>
<CORRECTION>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
Wrong math -- At the bottom of the chart on "How Long To Water" on Page K13 in 
the Nov. 18 Real Estate section, the formula should have read, "Total gallons 
required divided by total flow of emitters equals hours of irrigation." This 
formula was correctly stated in the story, but not in the chart. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
